OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with prolonged evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry with long clear
OL,8,Fspells and turning chilly, with a
OL,9,Ftouch of ground frost in sheltered
OL,10,Fspots. Winds mostly light but becoming
OL,11,Fbreezier along the coast and over
OL,12,Fhills.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FDry, fine and warm or very
OL,15,Fwarm, the sunshine perhaps turning
OL,16,Fslightly hazier later. A brisk breeze,
OL,17,Fespecially across hills and along the
OL,18,Fcoast, giving a noticeably cooler feel
OL,19,Fhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
