OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday, generally dry and warm or
OL,7,Fvery warm with sunny spells. Lighter
OL,8,Fwinds. Thursday cooler, breezy with
OL,9,Fsunshine and showers. Friday,
OL,10,Fcloudier, patchy rain moving east.
OL,11,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
